OL,3,CWales gets its first Reform UK council
OL,4,Cgroup as party targets Senedd elections
OL,6,FWales has its first Reform UK Council
OL,7,Fgroup, after three Independent
OL,8,Fcouncillors in Torfaen joined the
OL,9,Fparty.
OL,11,FOne of the party's newly-elected MPs,
OL,12,FLee Anderson, who represents Ashfield
OL,13,Fin Nottinghamshire, was there to
OL,14,Fwelcome to new inductees, calling the
OL,15,Fchange "superb".
OL,17,F"Labour in Wales are useless," he
OL,18,Fsaid, addressing supporters. "They are
OL,19,Fletting you down."
