OL,3,CWales gets its first Reform UK council
OL,4,Cgroup as party targets Senedd elections
OL,6,FTwo of the new councillors previously
OL,7,Frepresented Labour, and another was
OL,8,Fpreviously a member of the
OL,9,FConservatives, but before turning to
OL,10,FReform they were all Independents.
OL,12,FCllr David Thomas said: "We believe in
OL,13,Fthe party's focus on common sense
OL,14,Fpolicies, the economy, and the fact
OL,15,Fthat we can put local communities
OL,16,Ffirst, which aligns with our vision
OL,17,Ffor affective governance."
