OL,3,CWales gets its first Reform UK council
OL,4,Cgroup as party targets Senedd elections
OL,6,FCllr Alan Slade agreed that Reform
OL,7,Fcould offer communities like Torfaen
OL,8,F"common sense," as well as "cutting
OL,9,Fout bureaucracy, it's really as simple
OL,10,Fas that, there is money there, it's
OL,11,Fjust spent in the wrong areas".
OL,13,FReform failed to win any Welsh seats
OL,14,Fat this year's General Election, but
OL,15,Fcame second place in 13 constituencies
OL,16,Fin terms of vote share, outperforming
OL,17,Fthe Conservatives in those areas.
